         <abstract id="aspace_13a673d2bea8c4e47d43960cc0a631d4">The collection consists of posters from Argentina, Brazil, Costa Rica, Cuba, Dominican Republic, El Salvador, Guatemala, Nicaragua, Peru and Venezuela, regarding political, economic, cultural, and educational affairs.</abstract>
