      <scopecontent id="aspace_1d16aad042e438e674c759e6f432774a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of posters from Argentina, Brazil, Costa Rica, Cuba, Dominican Republic, El Salvador, Nicaragua, and Venezuela, regarding political, economic, cultural, and educational affairs.</p>  
